1
00:00:00,290 --> 00:00:03,130
This year's Tensho Festival Prince is...

2
00:00:03,130 --> 00:00:09,760
(This is the story of me and that guy,
and our 30-day quest to become the School Festival Prince.)

3
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,720
Mizukuchi-san, will you go out with...

4
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,180
Sorry! No way!

5
00:00:15,180 --> 00:00:16,390
I haven't even said anything yet...

6
00:00:16,390 --> 00:00:18,100
You were about to confess, weren't you?

7
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:22,020
Sorry,
but an unremarkable guy like you, Motomiya-kun,

8
00:00:22,020 --> 00:00:23,820
is totally not my type.

9
00:00:23,820 --> 00:00:25,320
But you said you liked kind guys...

10
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:28,860
Oh...
That's not what I meant.

11
00:00:28,860 --> 00:00:32,530
I like guys who are like princes!

12
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:36,290
Oh... I see...

13
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:38,500
Keep letting me borrow your notes, okay?

14
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:40,210
See ya!

15
00:00:49,630 --> 00:00:51,260
That was brutal.

16
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:53,300
Who's there?!

17
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:55,060
We're in the same class, right?

18
00:00:55,310 --> 00:00:58,100
(Isn't that the leader of the popular crowd?)

19
00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:00,730
You saw all that, didn't you?

20
00:01:00,730 --> 00:01:01,810
Pretty much...

21
00:01:01,810 --> 00:01:04,190
(The popular kids are going to spread this around
and make me a laughingstock...)

22
00:01:04,190 --> 00:01:06,570
(My college life is over.)

23
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:09,990
A guy who's like a prince, huh...

24
00:01:12,910 --> 00:01:13,950
Hey! What do you think you're doing?

25
00:01:13,950 --> 00:01:15,080
Hold still.

26
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:19,250
(If I fight back,
is he going to tell everyone what just happened?)

27
00:01:21,370 --> 00:01:22,460
Hmm.

28
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:24,420
Yeah, this could work.

29
00:01:24,830 --> 00:01:27,590
That girl has no taste.

30
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:30,510
Hey, you wanna team up with me?

31
00:01:30,510 --> 00:01:33,090
(Team up? Team up for what?)

32
00:01:33,090 --> 00:01:36,600
(But... as long as he keeps the secret that I got rejected...)

33
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:40,020
(At this point, I'll do anything!
I'll do whatever he says!)

34
00:01:40,020 --> 00:01:41,020
It's decided!

35
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:42,310
Wait... what exactly are we doing?

36
00:01:42,810 --> 00:01:44,980
We're entering this.

37
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:48,270
I'm going to turn you into a prince.

38
00:01:48,270 --> 00:01:49,730
Huh?
